(17, 'The Oberoi Cecil, Shimla', 'Chaura Maidan Road, Shimla, Himachal Pradesh 171004', 8, 206, 13, 2, 'This landmark Colonial-era hotel dating from 1884 and with views of the Shimla Valley is a 10-minute walk from Simla railway station and 1.3 km from the Mall Road.\r\n\r\nThe refined rooms and suites in classic Colonial style have marble bathrooms and Burmese teak floors, and are furnished in period antiques. Amenities include Wi-Fi (fee), minibars and flat-screen TVs. Suites add terraces and living rooms. Both 24-hour butler service and 24-hour room service are offered.\r\n\r\nBreakfast is free and served in the genteel restaurant, formerly a ballroom. There''s an atrium lounge bar, a kids'' play area and a heated indoor pool, as well as a spa with a gym.', 2, 'The Oberoi Cecil, Shimla1454507627-ab.jpg', '', 0, '77.1592', '31.1132', 'Y', 'The Oberoi Cecil', '', 'The Oberoi Cecil', '2016-03-02 17:30:59', '2016-03-02 12:00:59'),
(18, 'Hotel Royale Jannat', 'Aramwari Raj Bagh,near Foot Bridge, Srinagar, Jammu and Kashmir 190008', 76, 382, 14, 2, 'HOTEL ROYALE JANNAT which is placed on the bank of river Jhelum with Panoramic River View facing shankar-acharya temple .JHELUM River originates from a spring Verinag which is at the foot of pir panjal in the southeastern part of Kashmir valley .it then flows through Srinagar and wular lake and enters Pakistan through a deep ravine. The largest tributary of the Jhelum district. The river meets Chenab at jammu in jhang merges with the Sutlej to form the pajnad river, and ultimately surrenders to the Indus river at mithankot.\r\n\r\nKashmir is the” paradise of earth” and it is land of God. All knows Kashmir is the most attractive place of the world. Every year international & Indian tourist come to visit here and makes their trip memorable and amazing. Kashmir is increased the beautifulness of the India with unmatched natural wonderments and sightseeing spots. There are the number of tourist attractions like Houseboats, shikara rides on Dal lake, Gulmarg ,Pahalgam, Sonamarg and Mughal gardens , Adventures trekking, River Jhelum', 3, 'Hotel Royale Jannat1455114571-HR.jpg', '', 10, '13', '11', 'Y', 'Hotel Royale Jannat', 'Hotel Royale Jannat', 'Hotel Royale Jannat', '2016-02-18 09:45:56', '2016-02-18 04:15:56'),
(22, 'Hotel Armadale ', ' Waverly Road, Near High Court, Mallital, Nainital, Uttarakhand 263001', 0, 412, 31, 2, 'Hotel Armadale is one of the best hotels to enjoy an exotic stay on vacation. It is one of the best International class hotels in Nainital equipped with modern amenities. The visitors will be lost in the beauty of hotel and will be surprised to see the greenery all around giving them a peaceful essence of nature. Hotel Armadale Nainital offers you a luxurious and comfortable stay in its spacious rooms. The professionally hotel staff is at your service. The air conditioned rooms will help you to get off from your tiredness and boredom. You can enjoy long walks in and around the hotel and get lost in the bounty of nature. You are available with different accommodation options depending on your budget. The leisure and recreational activities are always enjoyable and can be opted on demand. Let us have a look on some of the best facilities provided by Hotel Armadale to its visitors.\r\n', 3, 'Hotel Armadale 1455857180-Hotel Armadale.jpg', '', 0, '116', '32.15', 'Y', 'Hotel Armadale ', 'Hotel Armadale ', 'Hotel Armadale ', '2016-02-18 23:16:20', '2016-02-18 23:16:20'),
(23, 'Jeewan Palace ', 'Hotel jeewan palace, Almora, Uttarakhand 263601', 0, 413, 31, 2, 'If you are on a vacation and intend to explore the lower Himalayas or simply want to spend a few days quietly enjoying serenity in the lap of nature, why not stop by our hotel? We will be happy to welcome you and help you fulfill the desires of your heart. ', 2, 'Jeewan Palace 1455858704-Jeewan Palace 1.JPG', '', 1, '1', '1', 'Y', 'Jeewan Palace ', 'Jeewan Palace ', 'Jeewan Palace ', '2016-02-18 23:41:44', '2016-02-18 23:41:44'),
(24, 'Chevron Ranikhet club ', 'The Mall Road, near Head Post Office, Ranikhet Rd, Airari, Ranikhet, Uttarakhand 263645', 0, 413, 31, 2, 'Chevron Ranikhet Club Hotel is centrally located in Ranikhet, Uttarakhand. The renovated Chevron Ranikhet Club Hotel was thrown open to its members on 01st January 2000. It was formally inaugurated on the 31st of December 1999 by its then President, Brigadier Rajeshwar Singh, VSM. The club hotel has been very distinctively refurnished to maintain and preserve the old world charm to which this structure so elegantly belonged.', 3, 'Chevron Ranikhet club 1455860316-Chevron_Ranikhet_Club_Hotel_', '', 0, '1', '1', 'Y', 'Chevron Ranikhet club ', 'Chevron Ranikhet club ', 'Chevron Ranikhet club ', '2016-02-19 00:08:36', '2016-02-19 00:08:36'),
(25, 'The Corbett View Resort ', 'Dhella Corbett, Near Dhela Village,, Naini Tal, Uttarakhand 244715', 0, 419, 31, 2, 'The corbett view resort offers you an stay in ac and mud hut cottages with thatched roofs in remote village of Dhela on the southern periphery of the JIM CORBETT NATIONAL PARK a stay in the wilderness close to protected areas and nature reserves. Spread in over 12 bigha of land our resort in Jim Corbett National Park which is surrounded by electrified fencing for your safety is a dense island of various varities of wild trees and plant growing naturally with cottages placed haphazardly all over. Mountain range of the Corbett and a seasonal pebbled river bed on one side and deep teak and Sal jungle on the other. The stay at Corbett view Resort in Jim Corbett Park gives you a memorable, insightful and cost-effective experience and also upgrades your knowledge and love for nature. The guides provided by the resort takes you on jim Corbett wildlife viewing and village walks. The surrounding/core area of the ashoka''s resort in jim corbett park offers a truly wild experience full of alarm calls, evidence of big cats and cats pugmarks.', 4, 'The Corbett View Resort 1455862278-The Corbett View Resort.jpg', '', 0, '1', '1', 'Y', 'The Corbett View Resort ', 'The Corbett View Resort ', 'The Corbett View Resort ', '2016-02-19 00:41:19', '2016-02-19 00:41:19'),
(26, 'Hotel Pine Grove', '3rd Cross Road Boulevard, Srinagar, Jammu and Kashmir 190001', 0, 383, 14, 2, 'Kashmir ,Jammu & Kashmir , Renowned for relaxed elegance personalized guest services and unrivaled ambiance ,the landmark Hotel Pine Grove is an Kashmir Luxury not to be missed .The Hotel Pine Grove is located in the vicinity of famous Dal Lake ,Boulevard ,Srinagar having scenic beauty of Shankaracharya Hillock at its rear and lush green lawn in the front and back of the hotel .It offers a luxurious Lodging and Boarding experience and is just steps away from the world famous Dal Lake ,Mughal Gardens ,Picturesque mountain ranges all of which make Srinagar ,Jammu & Kashmir famous .\r\nEach of the 40 guest rooms and 4 beautiful suites is individually decorated in luxurious, comfortable décor. The hotel offers all the services and amenities expected of a discerning traveler all year around', 3, 'Hotel Pine Grove1455863581-001.jpg', '', 0, '12.1', '11.1', 'Y', 'Hotel Pine Grove', 'Hotel Pine Grove', 'Hotel Pine Grove', '2016-02-19 01:03:01', '2016-02-19 01:03:01'),
(27, 'Apple Tree Resorts', 'Srinagar-Gulmarg Road, Batpora, Kunzar, Gulmarg, Jammu and Kashmir 193401', 0, 384, 14, 2, 'Apple Tree Resorts - At Apple Tree Resorts, we believe in complete hospitality. Located at lush green Srinagar-Gulmarg road, it''s one of the best hotels of Jammu and Kashmir.', 2, 'Apple Tree Resorts1456551780-appletreeresortmain.jpg', '', 0, '74.544557', '34.088863', 'Y', 'Apple Tree Resorts', 'Apple Tree Resorts', 'Apple Tree Resorts', '2016-02-27 05:43:00', '2016-02-27 00:13:00'),
(30, 'Bellmount Resorts ', 'N.H. Road, Idukki Dist., Munnar, Kerala 685612', 0, 420, 17, 2, 'Bellmount Resorts Munnar, where you will find a more meaningful way to spend your holiday. Enjoy pure luxury with world''s best specialities and all under one roof. Breathe fresh air, experience the joy of living with nature, enjoy our warm hospitality, then return to your everyday life, refreshed and rejuvenated.', 3, 'Bellmount Resorts 1455953026-bellmount-resorts_in_munnar.jpg', '', 0, '77.052994', '10.084672', 'Y', 'Bellmount Resorts ', 'Bellmount Resorts ', 'Bellmount Resorts ', '2016-03-01 08:41:34', '2016-03-01 03:11:34'),
(31, 'Hotel Grand Thekkady', 'Lake Road, Periyar, Kerala 685509', 0, 421, 17, 2, 'Hotel Grand Thekkady is a 32 rooms luxury hotel with premium facilities yet comes with an affordabel tariff. The hotel is nestled just off Periyar Wild Life Sanctuary on lake road. The hotel is a marvellous piece of Kerala architecture - an expansive lounge, luxurious rooms, coffee shop, roof-top restaurant, souvenir shop with graceful wood works and antic furn. Accommodation is classified   into Suites,Super Deluxe and Deluxe Rooms.The rooms are luxuriously done up with designer amenities to give you maximum comfort level.  ', 3, 'Hotel Grand Thekkady1455954182-Hotel Grand Thekkady.jpg', '', 0, '77.175382', '9.566257', 'Y', 'Hotel Grand Thekkady', 'Hotel Grand Thekkady', 'Hotel Grand Thekkady', '2016-03-01 09:37:06', '2016-03-01 04:07:06'),
(32, 'Samudra theeram Resort', 'I T D C Grove Beach, Kovalam, Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala 695527', 0, 422, 17, 2, 'Samudra Theeram, a gateway to the god’s own nature, is a shoreline resort settled in the midst of gorgeous coconut palms and enchanting region of Arabian Sea which offers a cherished haven for all of our guests. Samudra Theeram beach resort is located at Kovalam, one of the famous tourist destinations in Kerala, India. With its architectural excellence the resort offers ambient relaxation and comfort to enjoy the sceneries of marine, sunrise, sunset etc., from every room of the resort. Fenced by the miles of beautiful backdrop the resort offers you a perfect centre for revel in sea breeze, performing surfing and devouring delicious seafood and enjoy the tranquillity of marvellous oceanic blue. Our resort and its rooms are furnished with premier quality amenities blossomed with our two exclusive as well as attractive winter and honeymoon packages. We offer very extensive Ayurvedic packages, treatments and have Yoga with meditation classes for the relaxation of the body and mind to nourish the experience of serenity.', 3, 'Samudra theeram Resort1455955512-Samudra theeram Resort 1.jpg', '', 1, '1', '1', 'Y', 'Samudra theeram Resort', 'Samudra theeram Resort', 'Samudra theeram Resort', '2016-02-20 02:35:12', '2016-02-20 02:35:12'),
(35, 'Hotel Green Retreat', 'Middle Sichey, Indira Bypass Road, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Green Retreat, our hotel in Gangtok is located in Indira Bypass 4 K.M away from M.G Marg. Surrounded with mountains, valley and flowers. We offer all the modern facilities with best food round the clock, we will arrange for your sightseeing, other types of transport services and many other services. Being a budget hotel in Gangtok, Green Retreat offers you with hospitality care and high standard of services. Presenting you with care, comfort and our hospitality under one roof, as a best one among all budget Hotels in Gangtok', 3, 'Hotel Green Retreat1456204374-green-retreat.jpg', '', 0, '88.60734343528748 ', '27.33277326091505', 'Y', 'Hotel Green Retreat', 'Hotel Green Retreat', 'Hotel Green Retreat', '2016-02-23 07:27:42', '2016-02-23 01:57:42'),
(36, 'Hill Crown Retreat', '11, J.N Mitra Road, Chowk Bazaar, Below Sree Mandir, Darjeeling, West Bengal 734101', 0, 12, 1, 2, 'Our hotel in Darjeeling will offer you everything that ranges from budget to deluxe amenities & a comfortable stay. it is a Kanchanjangha view Hotel in Darjeeling, located in a with peaceful surroundings that is away from the rush, near Chowk Bazar which is the main market at Darjeeling that is 2 min walking distance from market and only 500 meter from Mall. Our deluxe rooms and super deluxe rooms will endow you with Kanchenjunga view with the refreshing breeze of the mountain, and a attached personal balcony with the magnificent view of the mountains. Best among all deluxe & budget Hotels in Darjeeling.\r\n\r\nWe also have an elegantly decorated restaurant at our hotel with a multi cuisine menu and splendid taste and aroma. We have incorporated the tradition and culture of Gorkha community, few famous movies like ‘Barfi’ has been filmed over here. Darjeeling is a land of beauty we try to make your holidays memorable by a royal stay at our deluxe as well as budget hotels in Darjeeling.', 3, 'Hill Crown Retreat1456204856-35082864.jpg', '', 0, '88.25758447631983', '27.030636790833846', 'Y', 'Hill Crown Retreat', 'Hill Crown Retreat', 'Hill Crown Retreat', '2016-02-22 23:50:56', '2016-02-22 23:50:56'),
(37, 'KayZee Hotel and Restaurant', 'Near Khidmat Trust, Regal Lane, Regal Chowk, Press Colony, Srinagar, Jammu and Kashmir 190001', 0, 382, 14, 2, 'It was the dream of my parents to build a luxurious hotel in the valley of Kashmir. which I fulfilled by making a star ranked hotel in lal chowk on the bank of famous river Jhelum ,situated in the heart of Kashmir. We have 30 luxurious rooms Banquet hall, lawn and car parking facilities available, our hotel has got elevator facility operating 24 Hours, The rooms are fitted with all modern facilities, direct dialing from room is available. Transport facilities it’s of all A/C and Non A/C vehicles are provided by us.', 3, 'KayZee Hotel and Restaurant1456550598-hotel-kayzee.jpg', '', 1, '74.815570', '34.072165', 'Y', 'KayZee Hotel and Restaurant', 'KayZee Hotel and Restaurant', 'KayZee Hotel and Restaurant', '2016-02-27 06:36:05', '2016-02-27 01:06:05'),
(38, 'Hotel Barzman', 'Leh Highway, District Ganderbal, Sonamarg, Jammu and Kashmir 191203', 0, 423, 14, 2, '“Hotel Barzman” Sonamarg,  welcome you to the Land of ‘”meadow of gold”, Mighty River Sind, Thick Forests & Giant Glaicers. Our Hotel is situated at on the bank of River Sind and is in the Lap of Himalayan Mountains and Glaciers at Sonamarg, which is on Leh Highway Near  to Sonamrg Taxi Stand.', 3, 'Hotel Barzman1456551232-Hotel Barzman 1.JPG', '', 0, '75.014382', '34.329840', 'Y', 'Hotel Barzman', 'Hotel Barzman', 'Hotel Barzman', '2016-02-27 06:35:36', '2016-02-27 01:05:36'),
(40, 'Pine Cliff Resorts', 'Circuit Road, Pahalgam 190019', 0, 383, 14, 2, 'Elegantly furnished and placed at one of the most convenient location of Pahalgam.Pine Cliff resorts in Phalgam, provides superior hospitality services to business and leisure travelers. Professional staff, modern facilities, luxury of comfort and cost efficiency are the prime highlights of this resort.', 3, 'Pine Cliff Resorts1456557967-Pine Cliff Resorts.png', '', 0, '75.108865', '33.820107', 'Y', 'Pine Cliff Resorts', 'Pine Cliff Resorts', 'Pine Cliff Resorts', '2016-02-27 01:56:07', '2016-02-27 01:56:07'),
(41, 'Hotel Highland', 'Near Golf Course, Laripora, Pahalgam, Jammu and Kashmir 192126', 0, 383, 14, 2, 'The resort is ideally located on a bank side of ‘Lidder’ river, Shopping areas etc are easily accessible from the resort. From Srinagar International airport it just takes one and a half hours drive and from main market Pahalgam city centre it takes 10 minutes drive.', 3, 'Hotel Highland1456559261-Hotel Highland.jpg', '', 0, '75.317781', '34.028783', 'Y', 'Hotel Highland', 'Hotel Highland', 'Hotel Highland', '2016-02-27 02:17:41', '2016-02-27 02:17:41'),
(42, 'Golf View Resort', 'Laripora | Near Golf Course, Pahalgam 192126', 0, 383, 14, 2, 'Golfviewresort Pahalgam is located near the Golf Course Pahalgam with an uninterrupted view of mountains with color video entertainment for your leisure in the rooms. This resort in Pahalgam is also equipped with modern facilities like EPABX, TV with modern DTH services and round the clock power facility. Food like Indian, continental and Chinese is also being served in the Golfviewresort restaurant. This is one of the best hotel among hotels and resorts in world famous hill station Pahalgam.', 3, 'Golf View Resort1456559945-Golf View Resort.jpg', '', 0, '75.317781', '34.028783', 'Y', 'Golf View Resort', 'Golf View Resort', 'Golf View Resort', '2016-02-27 02:29:05', '2016-02-27 02:29:05'),
(43, 'Hotel Grand Habib', 'Zero Bridge, Next to Modern Hospital, Raj Bagh, Srinagar, Jammu and Kashmir 190008', 0, 382, 14, 2, 'In Tracing professional way steps beyond hospitality ” Hotel Grand Habib ” is the place created on the bank of famous river JEHLUM and lies in the tranquil foothills of famous SHANKAR ACHARYA TEMPLE. the 56 roomed six storied building and sitting midest sprawling dulating lawn ringed by 15000 Sq feet surrounding area is the finest address in Srinagar, located just 10 Kms from Srinagar International Airport', 4, 'Hotel Grand Habib1456560626-hotel-grand-habib.jpg', '', 0, '74.944258', '34.125541', 'Y', 'Hotel Grand Habib', 'Hotel Grand Habib', 'Hotel Grand Habib', '2016-02-27 02:40:26', '2016-02-27 02:40:26'),
(44, 'Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency', 'Bodhi, Development Area Road, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Retreat Lamaz Residency, a deluxe Hotel in Gangtok, is located in a walking distance from M.G Marg, in a peaceful environment, with a magnificent view of mountain & valley. Lamaz Retreat offering complimentary Wi-Fi, Multi Gym, Multicuisine Restaurant, free parking with a lush green garden and a terrace, Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency is one of the best Hotel, among all Hotels in Gangtok near M.G Marg, located in Development area.', 1, 'Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency1456562837-Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency.jpg', '', 0, '88.611713', '27.337980', 'Y', 'Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency', 'Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency', 'Hotel Retreat Lamaz Residency', '2016-02-27 03:17:17', '2016-02-27 03:17:17'),
(45, 'Golden Star Continental Hotel', 'Pani House Rd, Vishal Gaon, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Positioned in the heart of Gangtok, the capital of Sikkim, Golden Star continental, Gangtok, is committed to offering superior hospitality by creating a home-like ambiance for both tourists and business travellers.Five minutes from M.G. Marg,', 3, 'Golden Star Continental Hotel1456563718-Golden Star Continental Hotel 1.jpg', '', 0, '88.610205', '27.324489', 'Y', 'Golden Star Continental Hotel', 'Golden Star Continental Hotel', 'Golden Star Continental Hotel', '2016-02-27 03:31:58', '2016-02-27 03:31:58'),
