(48, 'Hotel Renam', 'Arithang, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Tucked away strategically just five minutes walk from M G Road – Hotel Renam has its obvious advantages. The mellowed old world charm, the soothing quiet and the all pervading nostalgia are a welcome departure from the synthetic feels of many a star hotel. Precisely for this reason our hotel is rightly remembered as the lounge of the revisiting clientele. True to our style, basic comforts get top priority in our room. ', 2, 'Hotel Renam1456721999-Hotel Renam.jpg', '', 0, '88.610864', '27.332742', 'Y', 'Hotel Renam', 'Hotel Renam', 'Hotel Renam', '2016-02-28 23:29:59', '2016-02-28 23:29:59'),
