(50, 'Summit Norling Resort & Spa', 'Rongay, Near Central Jail,, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'At the head of a secluded valley on the North of Gangtok city is Summit Norling Resort, a place of replenishment and refinement. Enjoy the best of Sikkimese hospitality in our sprawling 3 acre resort with lush green lawns, a meditative pathway with a peaceful sound of the waterfall inside the resort, haiku-like bamboo grove and nibbling fishes in the pond. The subtle design of the Resort brings the outdoors in, inviting you to unwind and soak up the peace and quiet of the tranquil location.', 3, 'Summit Norling Resort & Spa1456723371-summit norling resort and spa.jpg', '', 0, '88.609658', '27.337136', 'Y', 'Summit Norling Resort & Spa', 'Summit Norling Resort & Spa', 'Summit Norling Resort & Spa', '2016-02-29 05:37:37', '2016-02-29 00:07:37'),
(51, 'Summit Golden Crescent Resort & Spa', 'Near Sichey Co-operative Taxi Stand, Lower Sichey, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Experience a new level of sophistication at Summit Golden Crescent & Spa. Located close to the heart of the city, the hotel offers all the services which are ideal for couples, adults, groups and business travellers. The hotel’s point of difference is its emphasis on appealing designs, a warm and welcoming environment with careful attention to details and personal service. All of the 28 Executive rooms and Suites have their own distinctive style and are complimented with eclectic furniture. The décor’ is a celebration of contemporary art and design with hints of the warm Sikkimese hospitality.', 3, 'Summit Golden Crescent Resort & Spa1456724151-summit-golden-crescent.jpg', '', 0, '88.609658', '27.337136', 'Y', 'Summit Golden Crescent Resort & Spa', 'Summit Golden Crescent Resort & Spa', 'Summit Golden Crescent Resort & Spa', '2016-02-29 00:05:51', '2016-02-29 00:05:51'),
(52, 'Summit Ttakshang Residency Hotel & Spa', 'Kazi Road, Near Power House, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Two minutes from M.G. Marg and spectacularly situated in the capital city of Sikkim – Gangtok, Summit Ttakshang offers five luxurious Suites, each with a private balcony looking out to the stunning panoramic vistas of the city and the remarkable Kanchenjunga Mountains. Each of the twenty-one Deluxe rooms and Suites are designed with contemporary elegance and style combined with the warmth of Sikkimese hospitality to make your stay comfortable and memorable in this mountain state.', 3, 'Summit Ttakshang Residency Hotel & Spa1456724839-summit.jpg', '', 0, '88.609658', '27.337136', 'Y', 'Summit Ttakshang Residency Hotel & Spa', 'Summit Ttakshang Residency Hotel & Spa', 'Summit Ttakshang Residency Hotel & Spa', '2016-02-29 00:17:19', '2016-02-29 00:17:19'),
(53, 'Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa', 'Vishal Gaon, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Nestled at a fantastic location, stunning view of the Gangtok city and a luxuriate feeling of a holiday amidst the majestic mountains, Summit Namnang provides an unforgettable experience to engage your senses.', 3, 'Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa1456725572-Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa 2.jpg', '', 0, '88.606037', '27.326818', 'Y', 'Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa', 'Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa', 'Hotel Summit Namnang Courtyard and Spa', '2016-02-29 00:29:32', '2016-02-29 00:29:32'),
(54, 'Hotel Yuma', '5, Laden-La Road, Darjeeling, India', 0, 12, 1, 2, 'Hotel YUMA, Darjeeling is another addition to the existing chains of hotel of JAGJEET HOTELS & RESORTS PVT. LTD. Set in the busy and recently rejuvenated central business district of Darjeeling is our Hotel YUMA. Conveniently located in the heart of the town, Hotel YUMA is the ideal place to stay in.  Holiday or on business trip, the Mall, taxi stands, local market, banks and entertainment centers are all within walking distance. ', 2, 'Hotel Yuma1456726827-Hotel Yuma.jpg', '', 0, '88.262675', '27.036007', 'Y', 'Hotel Yuma', 'Hotel Yuma', 'Hotel Yuma', '2016-02-29 00:50:27', '2016-02-29 00:50:27'),
