(56, 'Hotel Anand Palace', '5, Dr. S.M.Das Road, Darjeeling, West Bengal 734101', 0, 12, 1, 2, 'Capture the breathtaking view of the glistening Mt Kanchenjunga and rediscover the romance of a highlander’s life, cozily tucked up in the soothing ambience of Hotel Anand Palace -- where modern comforts and nature’s serenity are in complete harmony.Situated in the heart of a quiet town, this hotel with three star facilities has easy access to all modern comforts and yet captures the charm of a “heritage” Darjeeling.', 2, 'Hotel Anand Palace1456728300-Hotel Anand Palace 2.jpg', '', 0, '88.264762', '27.038785', 'Y', 'Hotel Anand Palace', 'Hotel Anand Palace', 'Hotel Anand Palace', '2016-02-29 01:15:00', '2016-02-29 01:15:00'),
(57, 'Summit Grace Hotel and Spa', ' Dr. Zakir Hussain Road, Near St. Paul’s School, Jalapahar, Darjeeling, West Bengal 734101', 0, 12, 1, 2, 'Just steps away from the hustle bustle of the Darjeeling town lies Summit Grace Hotel & Spa, with distinctive design, creating an ambience that is unique to travelers looking for ultimate pampering experience. Be swept away by romantic architecture, Italian design, exceptional luxury Spa facilities and impeccable service. The awe-inspiring view of the Kanchenjunga Mountains and the impressive bird’s eye view of the Darjeeling town from the Hotel, Summit Grace is a hidden treasure where you can experience the free- spirited atmosphere of this paradise.', 3, 'Summit Grace Hotel and Spa1456729137-Summit Grace Hotel and Spa 1.jpg', '', 0, '88.257069', '27.020127', 'Y', 'Summit Grace Hotel and Spa', 'Summit Grace Hotel and Spa', 'Summit Grace Hotel and Spa', '2016-02-29 01:28:57', '2016-02-29 01:28:57'),
(58, 'Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa', 'Daroga Bazar, Robertson Road, Near Mall, Darjeeling, 734101', 0, 12, 1, 2, 'Located in the heart of the town and 5 minutes walking distance from ‘The Mall’, Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa offers a heightened guest experience with its immaculate service, innovative design, endless dining variety and luxurious atmosphere. The most conveniently located Hotel in Darjeeling on the main intersection, connecting the lower market to the upper market, providing a majestic view of the Kanchenjunga Mountains.', 3, 'Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa1456730215-Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa 1.jpg', '', 0, '88.280179', '27.039531', 'Y', 'Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa', 'Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa', 'Summit Yashshree Suites & Spa', '2016-02-29 01:46:55', '2016-02-29 01:46:55'),
