(61, 'Hotel Parijat', 'Below Kalimpong College Ringkingpong Road-Kalimpong, Rinkingpong Road, KALIMPONG, WEST BENGAL, 734301', 0, 424, 1, 2, 'Parijat  is a family run hotel in kalimpong. It is located in Ring king pong Road that connects the main town to Durbin dara. It is more like a Himalayan Home stay with all the facilities of a standard Hotel. The perfect way to relax and enjoy your holidays. The serene environment will help you to indulge yourself fully in your recreational activities The Homely atmosphere and quality service is suited to all your needs.', 1, 'Hotel Parijat1456733414-Hotel Parijat.jpg', '', 0, '88.469453', '27.059356', 'Y', 'Hotel Parijat', 'Hotel Parijat', 'Hotel Parijat', '2016-02-29 02:40:14', '2016-02-29 02:40:14'),
(62, 'Summit Barsana Resort and Spa, Kalimpong', ' Barsana Road | Upper Cart Road, Kalimpong, India', 0, 424, 1, 2, 'Approaching Summit Barsana, you feel it. A sense of calm, here, in the unexplored wonderland called Kalimpong. Located 10 minutes from the market and in a serene and quiet part of the town, the Resort is mere sophisticated elegance. The color seems richer, the air fresher, and everything just tastes better at Summit Barsana Resort & Spa.', 3, 'Summit Barsana Resort and Spa, Kalimpong1456734240-summit-barsana-resort.jpg', '', 0, '88.463025', '27.059208', 'Y', 'Summit Barsana Resort and Spa, Kalimpong', 'Summit Barsana Resort and Spa, Kalimpong', 'Summit Barsana Resort and Spa, Kalimpong', '2016-02-29 02:54:00', '2016-02-29 02:54:00'),
(63, 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort', '13.5 mile, Echhey,, Rishi Rd, Kalimpong, West Bengal 734301', 0, 424, 1, 2, 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort, located in a rural environment of Kalimpong, yet closer to town, one experiences a feel of serenity, spirituality and comfort. The Resort has Fountain, Garden, Stone sitting Corner, Bamboo Huts, Art Gallery & Small Library with leisure activities, best among Hotels in Kalimpong. This Kalimpong Resort has different sport & traditional games like Badminton, Archery, Dart, Fun Ride (Swing) etc. This Kalimpong Resort has land area of 72 Decimal, largest open area among all Kalimpong Hotels & Resorts. Guest can access complimentary Wi Fi. Dhardo Retreat & Resort is a perfect place to stay for Couple & family with children & best Hotel among all Hotels in Kalimpong.', 2, 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort1456735331-Dhardo Retreat & Resort 5.jpg', '', 0, '27.066382', '27.066382', 'Y', 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort', 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort', 'Dhardo Retreat & Resort', '2016-02-29 03:12:11', '2016-02-29 03:12:11'),
