(65, 'Hotel Sikkim Aurora', 'Karki Dara, New Helipad, Pelling, Sikkim 737113', 0, 376, 26, 2, 'Nature at its most beautiful - that is pelling for you, where majestic snow-capped mountains herald your arrival to our HOTEL SIKKIM AURORA, situated near the Helipad, on the top to the town and offers peaceful environment and cool mountain breeze.The Hotel consists of 16 superb Bedrooms including Luxury suites and Deluxe rooms, Spacious Lobby in different floors, large Conference Hall. A warm welcome, a friendly smile, a gracious reception, personalized and elegance services, quality food of your choice.', 2, 'Hotel Sikkim Aurora1456736659-Hotel Sikkim Aurora.jpg', '', 0, '88.240033', '27.319772', 'Y', 'Hotel Sikkim Aurora', 'Hotel Sikkim Aurora', 'Hotel Sikkim Aurora', '2016-02-29 03:34:19', '2016-02-29 03:34:19'),
(66, 'Floret Hotel ', 'New helipad, Pelling 737113, India', 0, 376, 26, 2, 'Pelling is the leading tourist spot in west Sikkim You can experience impeccable waterfalls, soothing lake scenes, monasteries and picturesque villages to see and cherish the beauty of nature. We make accommodations easily accessible for you in Pellling. We promise the visitor most comfortable and memorable stay at Floret Hotel in Pelling.We provide a vast range of food varieties, right from Indian, Chineese dishes to traditional ones. Enjoy your food sitting in the view point of Mt. Kanchendzonga and make your stay memorable for ever. we are the only hotel in our category with the roof top restaurant for an amazing 360o panaromic view of the Himalayan ranges and its valleys.', 2, 'Floret Hotel 1456738893-Floret Hotel 2.jpg', '', 0, '88.240033', '27.319772', 'Y', 'Floret Hotel ', 'Floret Hotel ', 'Floret Hotel ', '2016-02-29 04:11:34', '2016-02-29 04:11:34'),
(67, 'Hotel Norling', 'Middle Pelling, 737113, India', 0, 376, 26, 2, 'The Hotel Norling offers a unique and personal tryst with the Himalayas. The Norling is professionally managed hotel which pays high emphasis on quality and customer satisfaction. Each room is different with subtle tasteful colours . A stylish property & is conveniently located in middle Pelling and is a great respite to travelers. Pelling is a small but beautiful hill station in west Sikkim. Located at an attitude of 6200ft above sea level.', 1, 'Hotel Norling1456739793-Hotel Norling 1.jpg', '', 0, '88.232730', '27.302054', 'Y', 'Hotel Norling', 'Hotel Norling', 'Hotel Norling', '2016-02-29 04:26:33', '2016-02-29 04:26:33'),
(68, 'Hotel Khangsar Villa', 'Upper Development Area, Near Brahma Kumaris, Development Area Rd, Sungava, Gangtok, Sikkim 737101', 0, 375, 26, 2, 'Sikkim’s capital is a city not to be missed. Vibrant, cheerful and warm, Gangtok is a perfect getaway from the pressures of big-city life, and a great launch-pad for all your adventures into other parts of Sikkim. Sample the hospitality of this lovely little hill city with the perfect arrangement at khangsar villa. Located in the peaceful residential environs amid the upper reaches of the city khangsar villa is the ideal place to unwind, rest and take in the sights of Gangtok as it rolls onward among the hills. Overlooking the iconic Rumtek Monastery hill, this is truly a home away from home in the heart of the mighty Himalayas.', 3, 'Hotel Khangsar Villa1456746579-khangsar-villa-gangtok.jpg', '', 0, '88.610751', '27.338391', 'Y', 'Hotel Khangsar Villa', 'Hotel Khangsar Villa', 'Hotel Khangsar Villa', '2016-03-01 10:38:56', '2016-03-01 05:08:56'),
(69, 'Summit Newa Regency', 'Pelling Rimbi Road, Lower Pelling, Near SBI Bank, Pelling City, Sikkim 737113', 0, 376, 26, 2, 'Bestowed with nature’s beauty, Pelling’s landmark of luxury-“Summit Newa Regency” welcomes you with a simple greeting “Namaste”. Celebrate and experience timeless beauty and luxurious comfort in pristine wilderness.', 3, 'Summit Newa Regency1456746887-Summit Newa Regency 1.jpg', '', 0, '88.240033', '27.319772', 'Y', 'Summit Newa Regency', 'Summit Newa Regency', 'Summit Newa Regency', '2016-02-29 06:24:47', '2016-02-29 06:24:47'),
(70, 'Himalayan Retreat & Resort', 'Upper Naku, Chumbong, Pelling, Sikkim 737113', 0, 376, 26, 2, 'Our Hotel in Pelling, Himalayan Retreat is nestled among hilltops. Pelling is a jewel of Sikkim where thousands flock annually to witness a wonder of nature: the Kanchenjunga peak. It is one of our prized specialities, not the hospitality but the view that greets you from our Pelling Hotels window. A majestic snow covered Kanchenjunga peak that leaves a lasting impression on the mind of every single guest who comes to visit us. Our Hotel in Pelling is one a kind getaway that boasts wondrous surroundings which leave you spell bound as best one among all Hotels in Pelling.', 1, 'Himalayan Retreat & Resort1456748113-Himalayan Retreat & Resort.jpg', '', 0, '88.240033', '27.319772', 'Y', 'Himalayan Retreat & Resort', 'Himalayan Retreat & Resort', 'Himalayan Retreat & Resort', '2016-02-29 06:45:13', '2016-02-29 06:45:13'),
(71, 'Hidden Hill Retreat ', 'Lachen Road | beside check post, Lachen 737120, India', 0, 425, 26, 2, 'Hotel Hidden Hill Retreat is a budget hotel in Lachen, surrounded with snow capped mountains. An ideal location for stay on the way to Gurudongmer Lake. Hotel offers clean rooms, In house Restaurant, private car parking space, common balcony, friendly front office. Our Hotel service staff try to make guest’s stay at Hotel Hidden Hill Retreat. This budget Hotel is best value for money among all budget Hotels in Lachen, North Sikkim. This hotel is well-suited for group, families & holiday travelers as a budget Hotels in Lachen, North Sikkim.', 1, 'Hidden Hill Retreat 1456749657-Hidden Hill Retreat.jpg', '', 0, '88.557739', '27.716667', 'Y', 'Hidden Hill Retreat ', 'Hidden Hill Retreat ', 'Hidden Hill Retreat ', '2016-02-29 07:10:57', '2016-02-29 07:10:57'),
