(75, 'Hotel Lachung Continental', 'Katow Road, Sarchok, Lachung, Sikkim 737120', 0, 426, 26, 2, 'The more beauty we perceive the more we grow. Such is the reflection of yourself at Hotel Lachung Continental.\r\nThe beauty of the Hotel and its comfort are a thing of ecstacy. while the idea of committing your vacation to sight seeing might be as attractive, you will be significantly drawn  to come back to your room at the Hotel Lachung Continental and put up your feet. Let us pamper you with modern facilities and the tastiest vegetarian food.\r\n', 1, 'Hotel Lachung Continental1456815833-Hotel Lachung Continental.jpg', '', 0, '88.742972', '27.689057', 'Y', 'Hotel Lachung Continental', 'Hotel Lachung Continental', 'Hotel Lachung Continental', '2016-03-01 01:33:53', '2016-03-01 01:33:53'),
(76, 'Tenzing Retreat', 'Thomchi, Near SBI, Lachung, Sikkim 737120', 0, 426, 26, 2, 'Tenzing retreat located in the beautiful village of Lachung in North Sikkim. This Lachung hotel surrouned by lush green terrain that will soothe your soul and uplift you mind to great peaceful reveries which you will experience nowhere else. Among all best Hotels in Lachung, Tenzing Retreat offers you with a splendid view of the snow capped mountain from room. Our Hotel has common balcony and a restaurant with power back up facility. This Retreat will make you want to stay forever as the homely feeling here is all too strong to ignore. Lachung is the gateway to the Yumthang Valley. Winters find snow covering most of the Hotels in Lachung village. Yumthang valley, the view being something that should not be missed, which is the best in our Hotel in Lachung.', 1, 'Tenzing Retreat1456816948-tenzing_retreat.jpg', '', 0, '88.742972', '27.689057', 'Y', 'Tenzing Retreat', 'Tenzing Retreat', 'Tenzing Retreat', '2016-03-01 01:52:28', '2016-03-01 01:52:28'),
(77, 'Apple Valley Inn', 'Faka, Lachung, Sikkim 737120', 0, 426, 26, 2, 'Apple Valley Inn is a unique property with stand alone cottage in Lachung and the only such property of the region North Sikkim. The cottage is situated in the Lachung Valley with spread out area and is devoted to the hospitality principle tourist satisfaction. We sincerely believe that all our tourists deserve affordable and quality accommodation / Lodging when on tour. To develop a relation with our guests, we strive for excellence in everything we do. We have combined old world charm and modern comfort in each of the beautifully decorated rooms. The rooms are all wooden structure, LED television in each of the room along with geysers. The stand alone cottages / accommodation are best in the region.', 3, 'Apple Valley Inn1456817609-apple-valley-inn.jpg', '', 0, '88.742972', '27.689057', 'Y', 'Apple Valley Inn', 'Apple Valley Inn', 'Apple Valley Inn', '2016-03-01 02:03:29', '2016-03-01 02:03:29'),
(78, 'Nest Resort', 'Munnar -Anachal Road Chithirapuram, Chithirapuram, MUNNAR, KERALA, 685565, ., Kerala 685565', 0, 420, 17, 2, 'Nestled in the Munnar Hills, this serene resort with a wrap-around porch is also 6 km from Rose Gardens, 9 km from Pothamedu Viewpoint and 12 km from the Tea Museum. Colourful, simply furnished rooms come with TVs and seating areas; some have balconies and scenic mountain views.', 2, 'Nest Resort1456820228-Nest Resort.jpg', '', 24, '77.090981', '10.016958', 'Y', 'Nest Resort', 'Nest Resort', 'Nest Resort', '2016-03-01 02:47:08', '2016-03-01 02:47:08'),
(79, ' Las Palmas', 'NH 49, Devikulam P. O, Munnar, Idukki, Munnar, Kerala', 0, 420, 17, 2, 'Las Palmas Munnar provides you with all that you are looking for ...Great  interiors..maximum mileage for your money ...and a thoroughly modern setup.Las Palmas is 150 kms away from the southern cities of Cochin, Madurai and Coimbatore. It''s the gate way resort for those coming from Madurai on NH 49. Tourists arriving from Cochin and Coimbatore may leave the crowd of Munnar town behind and drive up on the smooth NH 49 for another 6 Kms to reach Laspalmas. Being right on the Highway, it is extremely difficult to miss this resort.\r\n ', 2, ' Las Palmas1456821240-laspalma resort.jpg', '', 0, '77.059525', '10.088933', 'Y', ' Las Palmas', ' Las Palmas', ' Las Palmas', '2016-03-01 03:04:00', '2016-03-01 03:04:00'),
(80, 'Seven Springs Plantation Resort', 'Mankulam -Nirar Dam Trail, Mankulam Road, Letchmi Estate, Munnar, Kerala 685561', 0, 420, 17, 2, 'Just 15 minutes drive from Munnar Bus station to the resort through immaculately manicured tea gardens and a stream leading to resort is mind refreshing. Spread across cardamom plantation and deep woods offers forest environment is just 10km away from munnar town at Mankulam road in Letchmi Estate', 3, 'Seven Springs Plantation Resort1456822904-Seven Springs Plantation Resort.jpg', '', 1, '76.872096', '10.128748', 'Y', 'Seven Springs Plantation Resort', 'Seven Springs Plantation Resort', 'Seven Springs Plantation Resort', '2016-03-01 03:31:44', '2016-03-01 03:31:44'),
(81, 'Thekkady Woods ', 'Anavachal Road, Thekkady, Kumily, Kerala 685509', 0, 421, 17, 2, 'Thekkady Woods is Forest facing with well appointed Suite, A/c and Non A/c Deluxe rooms, A/c and Non A/c Rooms and restaurant serving speciality Kuttanadan village dishes. A team of professionals in hospitality will assist you for all your needs.', 3, 'Thekkady Woods 1456824406-Thekkady Woods.jpg', '', 0, '77.161458', '9.603109', 'Y', 'Thekkady Woods ', 'Thekkady Woods ', 'Thekkady Woods ', '2016-03-01 09:31:16', '2016-03-01 04:01:16'),
(82, 'Blooming Paradise', 'Kumily Thekkady Rd, Thekkady, Kumily, Kerala 685509', 0, 421, 17, 2, 'Hotel Blooming Paradise, a much awaited delightful get away theme based hotel, invites you to stay where the emerald green forest wearing the Diamond Water Garland.Blooming Paradise is on the bank rocks of Periyar lake, Thekkady.', 3, 'Blooming Paradise1456825600-Blooming Paradise.jpg', '', 0, '77.171225', '9.599905', 'Y', 'Blooming Paradise', 'Blooming Paradise', 'Blooming Paradise', '2016-03-01 04:16:40', '2016-03-01 04:16:40'),
(83, 'Samudra Theeram Beach Resort', 'I T D C Grove Beach, Kovalam, Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala 695527', 0, 422, 17, 2, 'Samudra Theeram, a gateway to the god’s own nature, is a shoreline resort settled in the midst of gorgeous coconut palms and enchanting region of Arabian Sea which offers a cherished haven for all of our guests. Samudra Theeram beach resort is located at Kovalam, one of the famous tourist destinations in Kerala, India. With its architectural excellence the resort offers ambient relaxation and comfort to enjoy the sceneries of marine, sunrise, sunset etc., from every room of the resort. Fenced by the miles of beautiful backdrop the resort offers you a perfect centre for revel in sea breeze, performing surfing and devouring delicious seafood and enjoy the tranquillity of marvellous oceanic blue.\r\n', 3, 'Samudra Theeram Beach Resort1456826888-Samudra Theeram Beach Resort.jpg', '', 0, '76.976323', '8.390546', 'Y', 'Samudra Theeram Beach Resort', 'Samudra Theeram Beach Resort', 'Samudra Theeram Beach Resort', '2016-03-01 04:38:08', '2016-03-01 04:38:08'),
(84, 'Jeevan Beach Resort', 'Hawa Beach, Kovalam, Vizhinjam, Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala 695521', 0, 422, 17, 2, 'The Jeevan Beach Resort hosts tourists at the heart of Kovalam "the paradise of south India". Kovalam is an internationally renowned beach with three adjacent crescent beaches. It has been a favorite haunt of tourists, especially Europeans, since the 1970s.  A massive rocky promontory on the beach has created a beautiful bay of calm waters ideal for sea bathing.', 3, 'Jeevan Beach Resort1456828438-Jeevan Beach Resort.jpg', '', 0, '76.978708', '8.400398', 'Y', 'Jeevan Beach Resort', 'Jeevan Beach Resort', 'Jeevan Beach Resort', '2016-03-01 05:03:58', '2016-03-01 05:03:58'),
(85, 'Park International', 'Light House Rd, Kovalam, Thiruvananthapuram, Kerala 695521\r\n', 0, 422, 17, 2, 'Kovalam Beach is one of the most sought-after destination in the state of Kerala. Since its discovery the place has been counted as a popular hangout zone for the domestic and foreign tourists in India. The beaches that lies stretched out here are discontinuous and often in strings.These beached, shaped like crescent are main hotspots in the town.', 2, 'Park International1456829350-Park International.jpg', '', 0, '76.982406', '8.383590', 'Y', 'Park International', 'Park International', 'Park International', '2016-03-01 05:19:10', '2016-03-01 05:19:10'),
(86, 'Sisir Palace Hotel', 'Thathampally, Alappuzha, Kerala 688013', 0, 294, 17, 2, 'Alappuzha, The city of coir canals and bridges. Once the world reputed ” Venice of the East” is now undergoing metamorphosis into a “Tourist Paradise.” This antique town is adorned with a glittering jewel by name “SISIR PALACE”', 2, 'Sisir Palace Hotel1456833009-hotel-sisir-palace-.jpg', '', 0, '76.347810', '9.506488', 'Y', 'Sisir Palace Hotel', 'Sisir Palace Hotel', 'Sisir Palace Hotel', '2016-03-01 06:20:09', '2016-03-01 06:20:09');
