(92, 'Rema Resort', 'Paro Rimphakha | Paro Bhutan, Paro, Bhutan', 0, 429, 37, 20, 'Rema Resort located on a hill top overlooking the valley of paro offers an ideal space for any visitors looking for a quiet and peaceful place to stay.The overall Structure of the reasort is designed to provide a purely Bhutanese way of life with an Impeccable Happiness.It offers a unique Opportunity to experience  the Bhutanes farm life with all the modern amenities the very few other reasort offer.Rema Resort is managed and operated by a team of staff who are friendly and demonstrating the highest level of hospitality.  ', 3, 'Rema Resort1456900211-rema-resort.jpg', '', 0, '89.416652', '27.428595', 'Y', 'Rema Resort', 'Rema Resort', 'Rema Resort', '2016-03-02 06:31:54', '2016-03-02 01:01:54'),
(93, 'Soanm Trophel', 'Bridge, Paro, Bhutan', 0, 429, 37, 20, 'Sonam Trophel started its journey into the hospitality industry in 1991 with the establishment of Sonam Trophel Restaurant, a name synonymous in the restaurant & catering sector in Bhutan, lt is also featured in almost all the travel brochures and guide books on the country including the Lonely Planet.Over the years we have expanded and ventured into affiliated areas with the establishment of Hotel Sonam Trophel, a 10 roomed affordable luxury hotel located in the heart of Paro Town The traditionally crafted hotel is equipped with all modern amenities and we also take pride in our 2 Restaurants in Paro which has over the years made a mark in the tourism sphere in Bhutan. Hotel is ideally located in the heart of the city. Sonam Trophel is a familiar and distinctive landmark, traditional wooden architect & paintings apart from the glass and concrete conformity of other hotels.Hotel Sonam Trophel is a fine budget hotel in Paro that offers modern comforts to its guests at a price they can easily afford. International airports in Paro is located at a distance of 4 km. respectively while the city bus station lies at just apposite from hotel\r\n', 2, 'Soanm Trophel1456901229-Soanm Trophel.jpg', '', 0, '89.417946', '27.430110', 'Y', 'Soanm Trophel', 'Soanm Trophel', 'Soanm Trophel', '2016-03-02 01:17:09', '2016-03-02 01:17:09'),
(94, 'Galing Resort', 'Galing Resort,Tshemdona, Paro, Bhutan', 0, 429, 37, 20, 'Galling resort is a deluxe resort located in Paro on a gentle slope overlooking picturesque Paro valley. The resort is 15 minutes away from Paro airport and 5 minutes from Paro town. It offers deluxe rooms as well as suits for guests. It is a relatively new property that is gaining popularity fast amongst Indian as well as international visitors. Offering modern comfort and Bhutan tradition, Galling Resort takes pride to be the hotel of choice. It is perched along the ridge facing the valley amidst the woods.', 3, 'Galing Resort1456902594-Galing Resort.jpg', '', 0, '90.433601', '27.514162', 'Y', 'Galing Resort', 'Galing Resort', 'Galing Resort', '2016-03-02 01:39:54', '2016-03-02 01:39:54'),
