el Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Anything which is not include in the inclusion</li>\r\n	<li>3.625 % Govt. Service Tax Extra</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '50% of the package cost at the time of booking confirmation.<br />\r\nBalace 50% of the package cost 8 days prior to the travel date.', '<ul>\r\n	<li>From booking date till 21 Days prior to departure : 25% of the Total Package Cost</li>\r\n	<li>From 21 Days to 14 Days prior to departure : 50% of the Total Package Cost</li>\r\n	<li>From 14 Days to 07 Days prior to departure : 100% of the Total Package Cost</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Important :</strong> The booking stands liable to be cancelled if 100% payment is not received less than 07 days before date of departure.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<strong>DAY 1: &nbsp;Arrive Kathgodam &ndash; Nainital</strong><br />\r\nOn arrival at Kathgodam railway station meet &amp; assist drive to Nainital. On arrival check in at hotel. Rest of the free to explore the surroundings. Overnight at hotel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 2: Nainital (Local sightseeing)</strong><br />\r\nAfter breakfast, Full day is at leisure to explore the hill retreat of Nainital. It is blessed with scenic natural splendour and varied natural resources. Visit to lakes tour of Bhim Tal, Sat Tal, Naukuchia Tal , Snow point Mall road, Boating Club, Cable Car Ride &amp; Thandi Sadak etc.Later back to hotel. Rest of the day free at leisure.Overnight stay at hotel at Nainital.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 3: &nbsp;Nainital &ndash; Almora</strong><br />\r\nAfter breakfast, drive to Almora. On Arrive, transfer to Hotel. Later visit local sightseeing Deer Park, Kasar Devi, Mohan Joshi Park, Chitai Temple (8kms.), Simtola, Brightend Corner, Kamlimath Museum.Overnight stay at Hotel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 4: Almora &ndash; Ranikhet</strong><br />\r\nAfter breakfast, drive to Raniket. Check in Hotel. Later visit local sightseeing Hairakhan Temple, Chaubatia, Bhaludam, Jhoola Devi Ram Mandir, Mankameshwar, Upat and Kalika Tarikhet, Binsar Mahadev, Majkhali etc. Dinner &amp; Overnight stay at Hotel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 5: </strong><strong>Ranikhet &ndash; Corbett </strong><br />\r\nAfter Breakfast, drive to. Corbett. On Arrival , transfer to Hotel, rest day at leisure. Overnight stay at Hotel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 6: </strong><strong>Corbett (Local Sight Seeing)</strong><br />\r\nJungle Safari with trained nature guides for wildlife and bird watching, cycling, nature treks and fishing in the Ram Ganga River on demand (at very nominal charges). Overnight stay at Hotel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 7: </strong><strong>Corbett-Drop Kathgodam </strong><br />\r\nBack to Sweet Home with Lovely memory: After early breakfast, drive back to Kathgodam. On arrive Kathgodam, transfer to Railway Station. End of our tour services.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', 'Uttrakhand is a &#39;paradise&#39; for nature lover&#39;s and adventure sports enthusiasts. Mussoorie, the &#39;Queen of Hills&#39;; Nainital, the &#39;Lake District&#39;; Almora, the &#39;Switzerland of India&#39;; Ranikhet, Pithoragarh, Pauri and Munsyar', '2016-06-30', 1, 'Y', 'Uttarakhand - The Land of Gods', 'Uttarakhand Package ', '<meta name="robots" content="follow, index, all" />\r\n<meta name="google-site-verification" content="rd73NCmbOEiQ6HB6_UKxP0zkp9V5u4A0jUCxH1fyMW0" />\r\n<meta name="msvalidate.01" content="D29D07AB3800231EE10F0FD2410E816A" />\r\n<meta name="distribution" content="Global" />\r\n<meta name="doc-type" content="Public"/>\r\n<meta name="classification" content="travel" />\r\n', 'Uttarakhand Package ', 'Uttarakhand Discounted Package ', 'Y', '2016-03-02 17:24:35', '2016-03-02 11:54:35'),
