ganeshtok,Flower show, Dro-dul Chorten &amp; Institute of Tibetology-afternoon proceed to darjeeling-overnight at darjeeling.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>DAY 04: Gangtok &ndash; Namchi - Drop Bagdogra/NJP</strong><br />\r\nAfter breakfast check-out to the hotel &nbsp;<strong>Back to Sweet Home with Lovely memory</strong>: &nbsp;Drive to Bagdogra/NJP in time for flight/train to onward destination.', 'If you want to see nature&#39;s real beauty then a visit to North East India is a must. Consisting of 7 states also called &#39;Seven Sisters&#39; North East India has some real surprises for the travelers coming here. Not so much established on the travelers map, yet the North Eastern India, has its own charm that will sweep you off your feet. Come here for once and loose yourself in its charismatic magic.<br />\r\nNorth East India Tourism holds various tourist attractions and famous places to visit that you are going to know in this North East India Travel Info Guide.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '2016-07-28', 1, 'Y', 'North East Delight 03Night/04Day - Summer Special ', 'North East Delight 03Night/04Day - Summer Special ', '<meta name="robots" content="follow, index, all" />\r\n<meta name="google-site-verification" content="rd73NCmbOEiQ6HB6_UKxP0zkp9V5u4A0jUCxH1fyMW0" />\r\n<meta name="msvalidate.01" content="D29D07AB3800231EE10F0FD2410E816A" />\r\n<meta name="distribution" content="Global" />\r\n<meta name="doc-type" content="Public"/>\r\n<meta name="classification" content="travel" />\r\n<meta property="og:title" content="Sikkim Holiday Packages - Book Gangtok Packages, Sikkim Vacations and Tour Packages with MyTravelDesk.in, India" />', 'North East Delight 03Night/04Day - Summer Special ', 'North East Delight 03Night/04Day - Summer Special ', 'Y', '2016-03-02 17:22:20', '2016-03-02 11:52:20');
